  "time_ut": 1659327182,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0b88.\u0baa\u0bbf.\u0b9f\u0bbf.\u0baa\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "EPTP welcomed Ranil's invitation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Douglas Devananda, Minister of Maritime Affairs and Secretary General of the Elam People's Democratic Party, has said that all the parties should come forward to overcome the political corruption among themselves and come forward to act as a united front in order to recover from the challenging situation in which all the people of Sri Lanka have faced great economic crises.",
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe has sent a written invitation to all the parties saying that the best results can be achieved by forming an all-party government to face the political and economic crises facing the country and moving forward.",
        "EPTP not only welcomes the call of the President but also contributes to the realization of that objective.",
        "In this situation, we as a nation must move forward by taking part in the all-party government and devising plans to win the political aspirations of the Tamil people who have suffered losses in many ways in the face of deadly war violence for more than three decades.",
        "Therefore, Tamil political parties should correctly predict the current political climate of Sri Lanka and take decisions.",
        "If they welcome the all-party government while giving it contradictory conditions and take decisions with the intention of seeking political gain from the confusion, it will once again result in the political defeat of the Tamil people.",
        "Therefore, the other Tamil parties should give up their political trend which is not suitable for the times, and realize that it is the need of the time to come to the practical and viable political method that we as EPDP have been saying in his press release. (R)"
      ],
